data.description:
Lovely 1960's ranch style home in highly desirable College Park. Just one block from the intracoastal, this home has beautiful, original hardwood floors, a spacious floorplan, lots of natural light, French Doors,  and an amazing Lake Worth Beach location. Structural  upgrades include Impact glass and hurricane shutters, newer AC, newer water heater, CBS construction, and a high, corner lot. The 3rd bedroom, currently used as a Family room, has a private entrance that leads to an outdoor patio. The living room opens to a screen room that is perfect for outdoor dining and entertaining, plus there is an additional, private patio located on the east side of house. This is a great house that has a cool, eclectic vibe that lends to the best of south Florida living. Walking distance to the intracoastal and a short bike ride or drive to Downtown Lake Worth Beach, the beach, golf and close to all transit. **The Sellers have plans for a second bath that could be accessible from Family room/3rd bedroom.  
All measurements approximate.
